'''上城'''（Bairro Alto）是[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[里斯本|里斯本]]市中心的一个区。
 
约1500年，曼努埃尔一世的宫廷从城堡迁至[[商业广场|商业广场]]的王宫。国王强迫农民离开土地<ref>[http://webserver.cm-lisboa.pt/turismo/index99pt.asp?pa=ptihist.htm História da Cidade de Lisboa] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100713004910/http://webserver.cm-lisboa.pt/turismo/index99pt.asp?pa=ptihist.htm |date=2010-07-13 }}</ref>。今天，它的功能为住宅，购物和娱乐区。上城是里斯本最古老的地区之一。拥有几十个法多歌唱俱乐部。葡萄牙的所有主要报纸在这里设有办事处。卖淫相当常见。

1990年代以来，上城区发生了重大变化。里斯本市议会进行了广泛的维修，数十家新餐厅，俱乐部和时尚商店开张。许多年轻人来到该区。汽车禁止进入（居民和紧急救援车辆除外）。今天，上城是里斯本的青年文化和夜生活的心脏。里斯本的[[朋克|朋克]]、[[同性恋|同性恋]]、[[重金属音乐|重金属音乐]]、[[哥特摇滚|哥特摇滚]]、[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈音乐]]和[[雷鬼音乐|雷鬼音乐]]都在该区拥有自己的阵地，各自有自己许多专门的俱乐部和酒吧。白天的上城区是一个传统的区域，老年人购买杂货、年轻一代参观''Zé dos Bois''这样的艺术画廊、''Ler Devagar''这样的书店，或附庸风雅的礼品店。 

尽管警方努力消除毒品贩运<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.psp.pt/Pages/Noticias/MostraNoticia.aspx?NoticiasID=140 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2019-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511071552/http://www.psp.pt/Pages/Noticias/MostraNoticia.aspx?NoticiasID=140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，毒品仍在街头出售。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sic.sapo.pt/online/noticias/sic+tv/reportagem+sic/20050512+-+Trafico.htm |title=SIC Online - Tráfico |accessdate=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195845/https://sicnoticias.pt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 凶杀案<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.icare.to/news.php?en%2F2007-04 |title=I CARE - News - Internet Centre Anti Racism Europe |access-date=2022-02-12 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305131936/http://www.icare.to/news.php?en%2F2007-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.colorlines.com/article.php?ID=90 "Choose Your World": Race in Portugal and the New Europe by Libero Della Piana] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061031025805/http://www.colorlines.com/article.php?ID=90 |date=2006-10-31 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.tvi.iol.pt/informacao/noticia.php?id=799751 TVI, Televisão Independente] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080410122802/http://www.tvi.iol.pt/informacao/noticia.php?id=799751 |date=2008-04-10 }}</ref><ref>[http://ultimahora.publico.clix.pt/noticia.aspx?id=1291670&idCanal=95 Publico.Pt] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070522121800/http://ultimahora.publico.clix.pt/noticia.aspx?id=1291670&idCanal=95 |date=2007-05-22 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.correiodamanha.pt/noticia.asp?id=21927&idCanal=10 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195845/https://www.cmjornal.pt/?id=21927&idCanal=10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
和破坏警方财产<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.publico.pt/Local/lisboa-duas-viaturas-policiais-incendiadas-esta-madrugada-no-bairro-alto_1405588 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229154928/http://www.publico.pt/Local/lisboa-duas-viaturas-policiais-incendiadas-esta-madrugada-no-bairro-alto_1405588 |archivedate=2012-02-29 }}</ref> 在过去时有发生。该区存在严重的[[涂鸦|涂鸦]]问题，破坏了历史建筑，例如[[费尔南多·佩索阿|费尔南多·佩索阿]]去世的地点.<ref>[http://ww1.rtp.pt/noticias/index.php?article=283868&visual=26 Telmo Correia faz campanha contra graffitis no Bairro Alto, diz que abandona AR se ganhar câmara - RTP Notícias] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210125245/http://ww1.rtp.pt/noticias/index.php?article=283868&visual=26 |date=2012-02-10 }}</ref>。

自2008年11月1日起，上城的所有酒吧必须在2点关门，以免噪音扰民<ref>[http://jn.sapo.pt/paginainicial/pais/concelho.aspx?Distrito=Lisboa&Concelho=Lisboa&Option=Interior&content_id=1037584]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。但是，到2009年8月1日，酒吧允许开业到凌晨3:00<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.correiomanha.pt/noticia.aspx?channelid=00000021-0000-0000-0000-000000000021&contentid=E8242F7C-0F1D-4098-B6D8-954C35378481 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195845/https://www.cmjornal.pt/ExportChannelLastContents?channelid=00000021-0000-0000-0000-000000000021&contentid=E8242F7C-0F1D-4098-B6D8-954C35378481 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。全市新批1200万[[欧元|欧元]]项目，以改善该区的外观和安全，即解决涂鸦问题
